description:
Travel to alternate dimensions with hosts Frankey Smith, Tyler Coates, and comic correspondent Coy Jandreau! From Jet Li’s The One to Everything Everywhere All at Once, the crew ranks their favorite multiverse stories. Then, they break down Peacemaker Season 2 Episodes 5 & 6 - covering brutal fight scenes, shocking twists, and game-changing reveals inside the DCU. Plus, discover must-read comic book picks and upcoming TV highlights every DC fan needs to know. 

Subscribe for weekly DC Studios deep dives, behind-the-scenes insights, and the ultimate guide to the DC Universe on Max.

description:
James Gunn returns with co-hosts Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt) and Steve Agee (John Economos) on Peacemaker: The Official Podcast to break down every shocking moment from Season 2, Episode 6. Joining them are Co-Executive Producer Lars Winther, Cinematographer Sam McCurdy, and DC Studios’ Galen Vaisman for an inside look at the making of this explosive episode. 
 
From Peacemaker’s jaw-dropping discoveries on an alternate Earth to the biggest character reveals, behind-the-scenes challenges, and hilarious on-set stories - you’ll get the ultimate insider perspective on how this episode came together. 

If you love DC, superhero shows or just want to know how James Gunn and the team bring Peacemaker to life, this deep dive is for you.
